{"tid":627594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賭王何鴻燊將退任澳博主席 女何超鳳接棒","createTime":"2018-04-13T06:21:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T11:04:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf9416e99f1d5d436506fa647dd2f0cce1a1795","tid":627594,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:21:17.000Z","msg":"（法新社香港13日電） 澳門博彩控股公司昨天深夜 宣布，高齡96歲的董事會主席何鴻燊將於6月的股東年 會結束後卸任，由二房千金何超鳳接班。有澳門賭王稱 號的何鴻燊將獲公司委任為榮譽主席。 何鴻燊被尊為澳門博彩業「教父」，這個位於華南 沿岸的前葡萄牙殖民地能夠搖身一變成為世界博彩業重 鎮，營收超越美國賭城拉斯維加斯，他是關鍵人物。 澳博控股預定6月12日舉行股東年會，何鴻燊將在 會議結束後退休，轉任榮譽主席。 何鴻燊去年已卸下設在香港的信德集團行政主席職 位，交棒給二房長女何超瓊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/t2LskCvIJBZqhzHN8whcpg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzY4O2g9NjMyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/afp/int0001b.180413070502.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Ft2LskCvIJBZqhzHN8whcpg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzY4O2g9NjMyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fafp%2Fint0001b.180413070502.jpg&h=72ba66d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B3%AD%E7%8E%8B%E4%BD%95%E9%B4%BB%E7%87%8A%E5%B0%87%E9%80%80%E4%BB%BB%E6%BE%B3%E5%8D%9A%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E5%A5%B3%E4%BD%95%E8%B6%85%E9%B3%B3%E6%8E%A5%E6%A3%92-230502003.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25B3%25AD%25E7%258E%258B%25E4%25BD%2595%25E9%25B4%25BB%25E7%2587%258A%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258D%259A%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BD%2595%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%25B3%25B3%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%25A3%2592-230502003.html&d=PIP6CtNqzdV40iPEgTS2v8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e9d3668f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B3%AD%E7%8E%8B%E4%BD%95%E9%B4%BB%E7%87%8A%E5%B0%87%E9%80%80%E4%BB%BB%E6%BE%B3%E5%8D%9A%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E5%A5%B3%E4%BD%95%E8%B6%85%E9%B3%B3%E6%8E%A5%E6%A3%92-230502003.html</a>"},{"pid":"4