:"2018-04-13T23:41:20.000Z","msg":"講到澳門賭業賺錢係因為佢噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食正支那人啲暴發又鍾意賭嘅水之嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:34:31.000Z","msg":"佢係澳門開放賭權之前已經開賭啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有份推動澳門博彩業發展同開放賭權㗎，冇佢冇宜家澳門咁風光呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你句食正XXX水套用係任何成功例子都得啦on9，咁你睇得咁通透唔去食XXX條水？不斷有新富豪出緊黎，唔好同我講以前點點點，宜家點點點"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:07:10.000Z","msg":"你都識講佢放賭權之前都有開賭啦<br />\n噉係咪佢開賭先令到人識賭呀，佢發明賭術定發明賭場呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有依個行業就一定有人會發出嚟㗎啦，再者你最多話佢勁在壟斷到，但話因為佢先令賭業賺錢就絕對係神化。本身都有賭業係爭在邊個發大之嘛，佢的確係食正條水發出嚟，而唔係因為佢而令到依個行業發出嚟，不爭嘅事實。<br />\n再者澳門嘅賭業做到噉大係因為國家政策禁賭，再加上支那多暴發戶同鍾意賭，畀著全世界賭業嘅成功都係靠依班人，而唔係靠個老闆。造神出嚟好咩？會顯得自己好似富貴啲？定唔想驚有人串你「講到咁勁你搵唔搵到呀」依啲咁無聊又廢嘅串人句子呀？聽到厭晒啦<br />\n唔好用支那人思想，批評佢個記者寫得唔準確都要好似主子俾人侵犯噉，又要用，「評馬要識跑馬」，我唔發就唔可以評個記者講錯嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1d4d04cb5ead7288a71bee70f3470f27562bb6","tid":627594,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9820fb4c5d7fe9e6d6ccbed336556b872057f03","tid":627594,"uid":5375,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:22:28.000Z","msg":"燊哥好人黎 智者<br />\n有無人po返佢n前年訪問片 佢公開叫大家千奇唔好賭錢，一定輸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:14:38.000Z","msg":"有啲思考嘅人都知賭係機會率上一啲係輸<br />\n賭都係揮霍錢嚟換快感，係服務嚟<br />\n智者佢就一定係㗎啦，以佢嘅經驗同知識，但一定唔係因為佢叫人唔好賭而顯得佢係智者囉"},{"pid":"3de4837ad9cdb3eb8a5814df552f19e840c1507e","tid":627594,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"382fb33cec2686b5b5fcf4edc062bc0c022124a5","tid":627594,"uid":134474,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:42:17.000Z","msg":"但人哋本來係高大靚仔有型有錢嘅超級筍盤<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/114211_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F114211_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c7f0ba7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/114215_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F114215_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d14cf47a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:16:55.000Z","msg":"果然係你樣子如何，你的命運也必如何<br />\n我諗如果佢唔係咁高大靚仔，都溝唔到佢果個有錢元配老婆番嚟"},{"pid":"d1f901cfd1423319140108a844bcdb7fe1d0250b","tid":627594,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:19:50.000Z","msg":"佢下面班所謂唔靠父幹既一早影晒合照相準備好分豬肉食"},{"pid":"85ebc51dd97ea8a73c9618771f97f850a234ea65","tid":627594,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3de4837ad9cdb3eb8a5814df552f19e840c1507e","tid":627594,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"382fb33cec2686b5b5fcf4edc062bc0c022124a5","tid":627594,"uid":134474,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T03:42:17.000Z","msg":"但人哋本來係高大靚仔有型有錢嘅超級筍盤<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/114211_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F114211_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c7f0ba7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/11